query:
INSERT INTO data_planes (
                        id,
                        mode,
                        region,
                        status,
                        capacity,
                        created_at,
                        updated_at
                    )
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
                    ON CONFLICT (id)
                    DO UPDATE SET
                        mode = $2,
                        region = $3,
                        status = $4,
                        capacity = $5,
                        updated_at = $7
